# Fixture capture: raw/ contains unscrubbed PII from live runs.
# Never commit. The scrubber (`bin/scrub-fixtures.ts`) produces
# `scrubbed/` — currently regex-only (emails/phones/SSNs/cards), which
# is INSUFFICIENT for real captures (addresses, names, order contents
# survive). Until the LLM-based scrubber lands (see OpenSpec:
# add-polyfill-connector-system/tasks.md "Fixture pipeline"), both
# raw/ and scrubbed/ stay local-only.
fixtures/*/raw/
fixtures/*/scrubbed/

# Local data + cache
.pdpp-data/
